    public class MinimalExperimentalParticipantPoolUpdater
extends MinimalParticipantEvidenceUpdater<ExperimentalParticipantPool>
implements ExperimentalParticipantPoolEnricher
    The participant pool enricher is an enricher which can enrich either single participant or a collection. The participant enricher has subEnrichers and no fetchers.
    Since:
